Package com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.ui

APIs for VisualVM UI.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataSourceView
    Definition of a subtab representing a concrete view of a DataSource in DataSource Window.
    DataSourceViewPlugin
    Plugin to an existing DataSourceView which adds an additional view.
    DataSourceViewPluginProvider<X extends DataSource>
    Provider of DataSourceViewPlugin for a DataSource.
    DataSourceViewProvider<X extends DataSource>
    Provider of DataSourceView for a DataSource.
    DataSourceViewsManager
    Class responsible for resolving DataSourceViews for DataSources.
    DataSourceWindowManager
    Class responsible for DataSourceViews manipulation.
    DesktopUtils
    Support for java.awt.Desktop
    PluggableDataSourceViewProvider<X extends DataSource>
    Extensible DataSourceViewProvider with support for customizations via DataSourceViewPluginProvider.
